{"TopicId":157376,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"How do I insert a picture on a forum?","CreatedByName":"Zerxal","CreatedById":175528,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-05T23:14:05Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Zerxal","CreatedById":175528,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-05T23:14:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"diomedea","CreatedById":93700,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-06T07:48:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCertainly one for a FAQ about this forum (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/154763-how-do-i/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ethis\u003C/a\u003E should answer it).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"munlander1","CreatedById":168560,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-06T11:19:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou do have to use the direct link for imgur.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"linuxgurugamer","CreatedById":129964,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-06T11:28:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUnfortunately, we still can\u0027t embed imgur albums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StupidAndy","CreatedById":171175,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-11T17:38:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis there a way to do it without imgur? using a different website?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-11T17:38:57Z\u0022 title=\u002203/11/2017 05:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 11, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by StupidAndy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-11T20:23:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222982722\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157376\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489253885\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022171175\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StupidAndy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, StupidAndy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis there a way to do it without imgur? using a different website?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFrom what did you get the impression you can\u0027t? Of course you can use another host. \u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EANY\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E host that allows hotlinking will do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-12T03:54:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPhotobucket, Postimage, and a number of others offer free image hosting, StupidAndy. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0Just copy their link into your posts.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-13T04:09:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust ensure that the link you are pasting into your post ends in .jpg, .png, .gif, etc. It has to be a direct link to the image file itself to embed properly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}